{"id":232966056,"title":"Mamba Out.","content":"I can’t believe...\n在這深夜，令人悲痛的消息⋯\n彷彿還在電視前吃著早餐收看Lakers Live，肩膀假晃動再一個完美翻身的步伐，接著熟練的後仰跳投，在空中畫出完美的弧線應聲入網，那是紫金色背號24號的黑曼巴 Kobe Bryant。\n祢在球場上展現的所有球技深深烙印在我腦海，祢永遠是我球場學習的典範，那精湛的球技，堅韌捨我其誰的強大心理素質，領袖風範。\n\n謝謝祢讓我愛上籃球，\n謝謝祢讓我知道籃球的樂趣，\n謝謝祢過去每一場比賽全力以赴的表現。\n當我還是個一股腦只會追逐著眼前籃球的小男孩時，同時也不停地追逐那紫金色的身影，當我對人說祢走了⋯⋯內心依然無法相信這一切事情的發生⋯⋯\nThank you, Kobe Bryant.\n\n\n1996年第一輪第13順位被夏洛特黃蜂選中\n背號8、24號\n生涯33,643分位居NBA歷史第四位、7,047籃板、6,306助攻\n5次總冠軍、2次FMVP、1次MVP、2次得分王\n11次入選NBA最佳陣容、9次最佳防守陣容、18次入選全明星賽、2屆奧運會金牌\n單場81分，單場得分位居NBA歷史第二\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e299c25d-3a0e-4c35-870a-340d9843b4be/full.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2d61e389-e8dd-420f-b8c2-86e25ad1bac7/full.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/96c7f90b-70fe-42da-bfa5-2f564db1ead0/full.jpeg\n#kobebryant #kobe #legend #basketball #8 #24 #小飛俠 #themamba #mambaout #rip #thankyou #kobebryantiloveyou #lakers","excerpt":"I can’t believe...，在這深夜，令人悲痛的消息⋯，彷彿還在電視前吃著早餐收看Lakers Live，肩膀假晃動再一個完美翻身的步伐，接著熟練的後仰跳投，在空中畫出完美的弧線應聲入網，那","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"863b960a-72a8-4479-80a2-b976275c002e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T08:19:26.602Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T08:20:09.069Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":8,"tags":[],"topics":["NBA","籃球","湖人","KobeBryant","Mamba"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"籃球","forumAlias":"basketball","school":"中華大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":8}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e299c25d-3a0e-4c35-870a-340d9843b4be/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2d61e389-e8dd-420f-b8c2-86e25ad1bac7/full.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/96c7f90